              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>jealous(y)</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is also possible to understand ὀφθαλμὸς πονηρός in {S:04002001500030} as meaning ‘stinginess’ (see {D:57.108}). See also {D:23.149}.</Comments>
